<h2 id="description_tab_h2" data-game-id="110" data-mod-id="13133">About this mod</h2>
<p>
This mod adds a craftable &#39;Dwemer Scouter&#39; and &#39;Dwemer Goggles&#39;. Forged with ancient Dwarven technology, these items give the user extra abilities in sight and perception.	</p>
<ul class="actions clearfix">
<li>
<a class="btn inline-flex button-share" onclick="sharebutton190932065.toggle()">
<svg title="" class="icon icon-share"><use xlink:href="https://www.nexusmods.com/contents/images/icons.svg#icon-share"></use></svg> <share-button id="share-button-190932065" onclick="sharebutton190932065.toggle()"></share-button>
</a>
<script>
	var shareConfig190932065 = 
	{ 
		url: 'https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13133',
